OL,18,     GDe Mortuis: Professor Rankin's
OL,19,     Gbuddies Wally and Bud stop by to
OL,20,     Gtake him fishing. Suspicions rise
OL,21,     Gwhen they find him in his cellar,
OL,22,     Gfilling in a hole with cement.
